column2: A video, in beginning, a man in black shirt comes and picks a bottle, a girl standing next to him. The girl then starts preparing salad. The girl is has long hairs, is skinny and wearing pink and white shirt. She is preparing it on white table. The camera position is at top, table occupies 70% of the screen and we can see only the body and hands of the persons. The man comes at the end as well and picks a bottle.
